Kabendera ni umunyarwandakazi wavutse muri 1978, ni umushoramarikazi wabaye umunyamakuru wa Radiyo na televisiyo y'igihugu  imyaka irenga 18<ref>http://www.bwiza.com/?Ni-iki-cyihishe-inyuma-y-ugusezera-kwa-Tidjara-Kabendera-wakoreye-RBA-imyaka-18</ref>. Ni umwana wa Kabendera Shinani nawe wamenyekanye kuri radiyo Rwanda , ijwi rya Amerika na BBC<ref>https://igihe.com/serivisi/special-pages/womens-month/inkuru/article/tidjara-amaze-imyaka-15-ku-ntebe-ya-se-shinani-wamamaye-kuri-radio-rwanda</ref>.

== ubuzima bwa Tidjara muri make ==
Tidjara yavukiye muri Tanzaniya aho yaje kuza mu Rwanda arangije amashuri muri Rugambwa Secondary school ndetse yiga itangazamakuru muri East African Training Institute (yafatwaga nkagashami ka Dar es Salama). ,Muri 2002b yatangiriye itangazamakuru muri Tanzaniya Arusha kuri Radio 5, 2003 nibwo yaje mu Rwanda atangira gukora kuri Radio Rwanda kuva ubwo kugeza 2021. Tidjara ni umubeyi w'abana 3
